+  chain:runtime    — in progress
+  chain:pallet     — blocked on chain:runtime
+
+ASPIRATIONAL (not started):
+  games:poker-engine
+  services:miner
+  services:validator-oracle
+  product:play-tui
+  platform:abstraction
+```
+
+### Known Defects Summary
+
+| Defect | Impact | Required Fix |
+|--------|--------|-------------|
+| `games:multi-game` false submit | Untrustworthy lane status | Rerun with real execution |
+| No `.raspberry/` state files | No durable control plane memory | Verify state path; run and persist |
+| Two manifests with unclear scope | Contributor confusion | Document bootstrap vs. full program |
+
+## Interfaces and Dependencies
+
+This lane depends only on the existing repo surfaces. It produces artifacts that all other lanes depend on for honest baseline truth.
+
+The lane does not modify any code. It only observes, documents, and judges.
